167
00:11:37,530 --> 00:11:38,573

168
00:11:40,325 --> 00:11:42,577
Qué emotiva escena.

169
00:11:42,577 --> 00:11:45,288
Es maravilloso, Inokuma.

170
00:11:46,331 --> 00:11:47,582
<i>Lo siento...</i>

171
00:11:47,582 --> 00:11:48,208


172
00:11:48,208 --> 00:11:49,959
<i>Perdónenme...</i>

173
00:11:50,710 --> 00:11:52,379
<i>Perdón, abuela...</i>

174
00:11:52,379 --> 00:11:55,382
<i>@@Yo...</i>

175
